{"tid":1175784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】立會宴請外國領事　梁美芬：從表情可知對方冀修例順利審議 (10:02)","createTime":"2019-05-28T19:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:06:59.000Z","uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e15e72ca476c4cf790f2413437db0b01e17f939b","tid":1175784,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T19:17:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真係犀利，表情都睇得出？ <br />\n可唔可以教下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvkRyAi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvkRyAi.png&h=cd13138b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會昨（27日）邀請逾20國駐港總領事與議員午宴。有份出席午宴的經民聯立法會議員梁美芬，今（28日）晨接受港台節目訪問時，便稱她在座的那一枱外國領事中，有人對修訂《逃犯條例》表示關注（concern），有人向她詢問「直上大會」後立法會議員還有什麽可以做，強調各領事均無明確表態支持修例與否。<br />\n<br />\n被問及是否有領事聽取她解釋後，明確表示已釋除疑慮，梁美芬形容領事們是很成熟的外交官，他們沒有明言此句，但從對方表情和回應可得知，領事們是希望有關修例是能夠在立法會順利審議。<br />\n<br />\n另外，公民黨郭榮鏗昨表示，多國代表主動向他提及修例問題和表達關注，同時希望政府作廣泛諮詢。他續稱，不少西方國家領事向他表示，正進一步向自己國家的外交部尋求指示，考慮下一步行動，包括需否提出外交照會或改變與香港的雙邊關係等。"},{"pid":"7a7ce12864872f47f226370efa9dc11b92260a8c","tid":1175784,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"最撚on9係新聞會報出黎<br />\n幫佢上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cada7f9452ac335e6a074b3dd4e270af71e5652f","tid":1175784,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T21:01:29.000Z","msg":"從表情就知啲老鼠唔撚怕佢..."},{"pid":"aec303c8ca1719d66bc14fda86e86a74f347800c","tid":1175784,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T21:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得盲人都會偷睇國家機密"},{"pid":"f35ba19e349e79502be2d88683e4c93559566f35","tid":1175784,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T21:17:46.000Z","msg":"應該打你一巴先聽你講"},{"pid":"cf7f284848ce6c120cb3cc1c8ab203c8250c4ccc","tid":1175784,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"張賤中已經俾人兜巴刮老鼠芬仲跳出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d306254cf7c34ad679f893220d6a9cb42c20f8","tid":1175784,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"真係屌佢都廢時 智障到連做人既資格都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9242eb9cc988dc3820b3f808a8d494fba7a38a","tid":1175784,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:16:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf393cc4755ead32c93aa224c0ce618c45176840","tid":1175784,"uid":187184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"表情強姦法"},{"pid":"8e913b7d2799ae31d5d65a5a5c341f1a05333ea9","tid":1175784,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:10:02.000Z","msg":"香港沉淪！<br />\n做律師講呢d！<br />\n仲有垃圾會收留"},{"pid":"a4d937744931714779edafc86318330f8cc3f93f","tid":1175784,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1hkvbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1hkvbV.jpg&h=38cd87b6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}